- **Three-step workflow**: Input tasks â†’ Rank each task â†’ View results
- **Four scoring criteria**:
  - **Impact**: How much does this task matter? (High/Medium/Low)
  - **Urgency**: How time-sensitive is it? (Now/Soon/Later)
  - **Effort**: How much work is required? (Easy/Medium/Hard)
  - **Confidence**: How confident are you? (Sure/Unsure)
